inputs.name: carpedalan-prod2020-micro-scaling-group-b631b03
inputs.userData:
#cloud-config
        repo_upgrade_exclude:
            - kernel*
        packages:
            - aws-cfn-bootstrap
            - aws-cli
            - nfs-utils
        mounts:
            - ['/dev/xvdb', 'none', 'swap', 'sw', '0', '0']
        bootcmd:
            - mkswap /dev/xvdb
            - swapon /dev/xvdb
            - echo ECS_ENGINE_AUTH_TYPE=docker >> /etc/ecs/ecs.config
            - echo ECS_CLUSTER='arn:aws:ecs:us-west-2:726278313509:cluster/carpedalan-prod2020-cluster-c408e30' >> /etc/ecs/ecs.config
        runcmd:
            # Set and use variables in the same command, since it's not obvious if
            # different commands will run in different shells.
            - |
                # Knock one letter off of availability zone to get region.
                AWS_AVAILABILITY_ZONE=$(curl -s 169.254.169.254/2016-09-02/meta-data/placement/availability-zone)
                AWS_REGION=$(echo $AWS_AVAILABILITY_ZONE | sed 's/.$//')


                # Disable container access to EC2 metadata instance
                # See http://docs.aws.amazon.com/AmazonECS/latest/developerguide/instance_IAM_role.html
                iptables --insert FORWARD 1 --in-interface docker+ --destination 169.254.169.254/32 --jump DROP
                service iptables save

                /opt/aws/bin/cfn-signal                     --region "${AWS_REGION}"                     --stack "carpedalan-prod2020-micro-scaling-group-7d4365a"                     --resource Instances

inputs.name: carpedalan-prod2020-micro-scaling-group-7d4365a
inputs.templateBody:
AWSTemplateFormatVersion: '2010-09-09'
    Outputs:
        Instances:
            Value: !Ref Instances
    Resources:
        Instances:
            Type: AWS::AutoScaling::AutoScalingGroup
            Properties:
                Cooldown: 300
                DesiredCapacity: 2
                HealthCheckGracePeriod: 120
                HealthCheckType: EC2
                LaunchConfigurationName: "carpedalan-prod2020-micro-scaling-group-b631b03"
                MaxSize: 100
                MetricsCollection:
                -   Granularity: 1Minute
                MinSize: 2
                VPCZoneIdentifier: ["subnet-7211e20a","subnet-394a0f12"]
                Tags:
                -   Key: Name
                    Value: carpedalan-prod2020-micro-scaling-group
                    PropagateAtLaunch: true
            CreationPolicy:
                ResourceSignal:
                    Count: 2
                    Timeout: PT15M
            UpdatePolicy:
                AutoScalingRollingUpdate:
                    MaxBatchSize: 1
                    MinInstancesInService: 2
                    PauseTime: PT15M
                    SuspendProcesses:
                    -   ScheduledActions
                    WaitOnResourceSignals: true
